Class Summary
ClauseBuilder Builder class to generate query criteria or set statement.
PersistenceManager<T> Generic PersistenceManager utility class that will be shared across various services.
QueryBuilder A builder class, which helps simplify building of complex queries.
Defaults are: paginate=true, page=0, orderByUpdateTime=true, desc=true, and limit=PersistenceManager.MAX_PAGE_SIZE.
